type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Taurus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Taurus\">TAURUS\u003C/span>\u003C/span>MULTISANNISHABEFACIAN\u003Cbr id=\"al10-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">10\u003C/span>COIUXIMUS\u003Cbr id=\"al11-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">11\u003C/span>PROPITIAM\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. suabiter | l.7 reg., orig. CASIANUSCasianus | l.8 reg., orig. mulierae | l.9 reg., orig. habe | l.10 reg., orig. coiuximus\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003659_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003659_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003659.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003659-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Orsi 1918\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3673-587X\">Maria Barbieri\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp> Il 16 Agosto Feridius servo della dea Cerere si unì carnalmente con tre adolescenti dei quali i nomi erano per legge Onesimus, L. Valerius Cassianus e Filumenus. Il solo Taurus (giacque) con quella donna, augurio ----.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>A substantial text incised in the wall of room of a Roman house (late Republican / early Empire according to Orsi), but in a phase of dereliction after the original use of the house in Orsi's view. The text is incised within an outline of a tabula ansata. In large letters below the main text is the word PROPITIAM. Several other graffiti are recorded in the same room.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1919.0057 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Orsi NSA 1918 58-60 fig.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1962 490-491 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 68 n.348 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[202,205,208,211,214,217,220,223],{"id":203,"html":204},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Barbieri\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>XVII K(alendas) Septemb(res) \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Feridius Cereris dominae servus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Feridius\">Feridius\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"atte